#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:1
msgid "模拟实盘模块总览"
msgstr "Overview of the simulated live trading module"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:3
msgid ""
"本章帮您在进入模拟实盘之前建立整体地图：能做什么、和回测有何不同、关键术语是什么意思、下一步该读哪"
"一章。"
msgstr ""
"This chapter helps you build a comprehensive overview before entering live trading: what you can "
"do, how it differs from backtesting, the meaning of key terms, and which chapter to read next."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:5
msgid ""
"亲爱的用户，若您已完成策略回测并想「按真实时钟」观察策略表现，本模块就是为您准备的。我们尽量用与回"
"测**同一套**策略代码，在本地模拟下单与记日志，让您在对接真实券商之前先走通完整链路。"
msgstr ""
"Dear user, if you have completed strategy backtesting and want to observe strategy performance "
"\"at real time,\" this module is for you. We try to use the **same set of** strategy code as the "
"backtesting, simulating order placement and logging locally, allowing you to complete the entire "
"process before connecting to a real brokerage firm."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:7
msgid "0. 适用场景"
msgstr "0. Applicable Scenarios"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:9
msgid "您已完成策略回测，准备进入**模拟实盘**阶段（尚未或暂不接入真实柜台）"
msgstr ""
"You have completed the strategy backtesting and are ready to enter the **simulated live trading** "
"stage (not yet or temporarily connected to a real trading platform)."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:10
msgid "您希望快速建立「配置 → 下单 → 成交 → 日志 → 排错」的整体认知"
msgstr ""
"You want to quickly establish a holistic understanding of the process from \"configuration → order "
"placement → transaction completion → logs → troubleshooting\"."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:11
msgid "您计划日后扩展真实券商（如 QMT），需要稳定的文档入口"
msgstr ""
"If you plan to expand to include real brokerages (such as QMT) in the future, you will need a "
"stable document entry point."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:13
msgid "1. 这个模块解决什么问题"
msgstr "1. What problem does this module solve?"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:15
msgid "统一解释模拟实盘里「配置、下单、成交、日志、排错」的完整链路"
msgstr ""
"A unified explanation of the complete process of \"configuration, order placement, execution, "
"logging, and troubleshooting\" in simulated live trading."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:16
msgid "降低从回测切换到 live 时的理解成本——避免「回测参数能跑、live 一启动就懵」"
msgstr ""
"Reduce the cognitive load when switching from backtesting to live testing—avoid the situation "
"where \"backtesting parameters work, but you're completely confused when the live test starts.\""

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:17
msgid "为后续扩展真实柜台适配提供文档入口，而不必从零摸索"
msgstr ""
"This provides a documentation entry point for future expansion to support real-world counters, "
"eliminating the need to start from scratch."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:19
msgid "2. 与回测的关系"
msgstr "2. Relationship with backtesting"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:21
msgid ""
"qteasy 的设计目标是：**同一套策略逻辑**既用于回测，也用于模拟实盘。区别主要在「时间如何流逝」和「谁"
"来做撮合」——而不是重写一套策略代码。下表帮助您在选型时快速对照；若您已熟悉回测，可重点看「模拟实"
"盘」列里与 live 相关的入口与成交方式。"
msgstr ""
"Qteasy's design goal is to use the same strategy logic for both backtesting and live trading. The "
"main difference lies in \"how time passes\" and \"who performs the matching\"—rather than "
"rewriting the entire strategy code. The table below will help you quickly compare options when "
"making your selection; if you are already familiar with backtesting, you can focus on the entry "
"points and trading methods related to \"live trading\" in the \"live trading\" column."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:23
msgid ""
"**各列含义**：**对比项**为维度；**回测**列描述历史验证模式；**模拟实盘（`mode=0`）** 列描述按真实时"
"钟运行的 live 模式。"
msgstr ""
"**Column Meanings:** The **Comparison Items** represent the dimensions; the **Backtesting** column "
"describes the historical verification mode; the **Simulated Live Trading (`mode=0`) column "
"describes the live mode running at a real clock."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:25
msgid ""
"**如何使用**：决定「现在该用哪种模式」时按行查；启动 live 时确认最后一行入口是否为 `mode=0` + "
"`qt.run(op)`。"
msgstr ""
"**How to use:** When deciding \"which mode to use now\", search by line; when starting live, "
"confirm that the last line entry is `mode=0` + `qt.run(op)`."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "对比项"
msgstr "Comparison item"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "回测"
msgstr "Backtesting"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "模拟实盘（`mode=0`）"
msgstr "Simulated live trading (`mode=0`)"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "时间"
msgstr "Time"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "历史区间上快进"
msgstr "Fast forward on historical intervals"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "**真实时间**按交易日历推进"
msgstr "**Real time** progresses according to the trading calendar."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "策略代码"
msgstr "Strategy Code"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "同一 `Operator` / 策略"
msgstr "Same `Operator`/Strategy"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "**同一套**逻辑"
msgstr "**The same set of** logic"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "成交"
msgstr "Deal"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "按历史价模拟撮合"
msgstr "Simulated matching based on historical prices"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "通常由 **模拟券商（simulator）** 按 live 价撮合"
msgstr "Typically, transactions are matched by a **simulator** at the live price."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "典型入口"
msgstr "typical entrance"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "`op.run_backtest()` / `qt.run(op, mode=1)`"
msgstr "`op.run_backtest()` / `qt.run(op, mode=1)`"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "`qt.run(op)` 且 `mode=0`"
msgstr "`qt.run(op)` and `mode=0`"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:34
msgid ""
"**Operator（交易员容器）**：您创建并持有策略的那个「交易员」对象；回测和 live 都用它，只是运行模式"
"不同。您可以把它理解为：同一位交易员，在「历史考场」和「模拟实盘考场」里答同一套卷子。"
msgstr ""
"**Operator (Trader Container)**: This is the \"trader\" object you create and hold for your "
"strategy; it's used in both backtesting and live trading, just in different modes. You can think "
"of it as the same trader taking the same test in both the \"historical exam\" and the \"simulated "
"live exam.\""

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:36
msgid "启动 live 的常见一行代码："
msgstr "A common one-line code to start live:"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:44
msgid "3. 您将获得的 capability（能力地图）"
msgstr "3. The capability map you will receive"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:46
msgid "以下能力在近年版本中逐步完善，目的是让模拟实盘**可校验、可拦截、可审计、可扩展**："
msgstr ""
"The following capabilities have been gradually improved in recent versions, with the aim of making "
"simulated live trading **verifiable, interceptable, auditable, and scalable**:"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:48
msgid "**配置可校验**：live 相关参数在运行前集中检查，配置写错时更早报错，而不是跑到一半才崩溃。"
msgstr ""
"**Configuration Verifiable:** Live-related parameters are checked before runtime, so errors are "
"reported earlier when configurations are incorrect, rather than crashing halfway through the "
"process."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:49
msgid "**风控可插拔**：订单在「真正交给券商」之前，可在本地按规则拦截（像下单前的复核台）。"
msgstr ""
"**Possible Risk Control:** Orders can be blocked locally according to rules before they are "
"actually handed over to the brokerage firm (like a pre-order review panel)."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:50
msgid "**拒单可审计**：被拒时可在日志里用规则编号和英文原因检索，便于复盘「为什么没成交」。"
msgstr ""
"**Auditable Rejections:** When an order is rejected, it can be retrieved in the log using the rule "
"number and the English reason, making it easy to review \"why the order was not closed\"."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:51
msgid "**券商接口可扩展**：统一 connect / submit / 轮询成交等接口，便于日后接入 QMT 等真实柜台。"
msgstr ""
"**The brokerage interface is scalable:** It provides unified interfaces for connect, submit, and "
"poll for transactions, facilitating future integration with real-world trading platforms such as "
"QMT."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:52
msgid ""
"**订单状态更清晰**：部分成交、全部成交等状态与累计成交量更一致，减少「界面显示和心里预期对不上」。"
msgstr ""
"**Clearer Order Status:** Statuses such as partially completed and fully completed are more "
"consistent with the cumulative transaction volume, reducing the discrepancy between the interface "
"display and one's expectations."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:54
msgid "4. 术语速查表"
msgstr "4. Terminology Quick Reference Table"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:56
msgid ""
"模拟实盘文档会反复出现 Operator、Trader、Broker、风控、产物路径等词。本节是**全模块术语 hub**：按主"
"题分组，供各章正文首次出现后回来查阅。您不必一次读完——遇到陌生词时用页内搜索即可。"
msgstr ""
"The simulated live trading documentation will repeatedly use terms such as Operator, Trader, "
"Broker, risk control, and product path. This section is the **module-wide terminology hub**: "
"grouped by topic, allowing you to refer back to it after it first appears in the main text of each "
"chapter. You don't need to read it all at once—use the in-page search when you encounter "
"unfamiliar terms."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:58
msgid ""
"**各列含义**：**术语**为英文名或配置键；**说明**为在 qteasy live 链路中的职责；**类比**用投资/日常"
"场景帮助记忆（类比与真实行为若有差异，以说明列为准）。"
msgstr ""
"**Column Meanings**: **Terms** are English names or configuration keys; **Descriptions** describe "
"the responsibilities in the qteasy live workflow; **Analogies** use investment/daily scenarios to "
"aid memorization (if there are differences between the analogy and real-world behavior, the "
"description column shall prevail)."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:60
msgid ""
"**如何使用**：先确定您卡在「运行主体 / 配置 / 订单 / 运维」哪一类，打开对应小节；根据当前问题（如"
"「拒单查哪」）在 **说明** 列找关键词，再跳转到 :doc:`3-risk-and-order-lifecycle` 或 :doc:`5-"
"artifacts-and-troubleshooting` 等章节。"
msgstr ""
"**How to use:** First, determine which category you are stuck in: \"Running Entity / "
"Configuration / Order / Maintenance,\" and open the corresponding section. Based on the current "
"issue (e.g., \"Where to check for rejected orders\"), find keywords in the **Instructions** "
"column, and then jump to sections such as :doc:`3-risk-and-order-lifecycle` or :doc:`5-artifacts-"
"and-troubleshooting`."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:62
msgid ""
"**示例**：您在 Shell 里看到 `partial-filled` 不懂 → 打开 §4.3 找到该行 → 得知是「部分成交」→ "
"到 :doc:`3-risk-and-order-lifecycle` 看状态流转。"
msgstr ""
"**Example**: You see `partial-filled` in the Shell and don't understand it → Open §4.3 and find "
"the line → You will learn that it means \"partially filled\" → Go to :doc:`3-risk-and-order-"
"lifecycle` to see the status change."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:64
msgid "4.1 运行主体"
msgstr "4.1 Operating Entity"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:66
msgid ""
"live 运行时，**Operator** 仍持有策略，但由 **Trader** 按真实日程驱动；订单经 **Broker** 受理。本表"
"覆盖从「策略容器」到「您交互界面」的主角色；不含具体配置键（见 §4.2）。"
msgstr ""
"During live runtime, the **Operator** still holds the policy, but it is driven by the **Trader** "
"according to the real schedule; orders are processed by the **Broker**. This table covers the main "
"roles from the \"policy container\" to the \"your interface\"; it does not include specific "
"configuration keys (see §4.2)."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "术语"
msgstr "the term"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "说明"
msgstr "Description"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "类比"
msgstr "analogy"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "**Operator**"
msgstr "**Operator**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "持有策略组、负责调度与信号合并的顶层容器"
msgstr ""
"The top-level container that holds the policy group and is responsible for scheduling and signal "
"merging."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "投资组合经理：决定何时跑哪些策略"
msgstr "Portfolio Manager: Deciding When and Which Strategies to Run"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "**Trader**"
msgstr "**Trader**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "live 模式下实际按日程运行策略、下单、写日志的进程主体"
msgstr ""
"In live mode, the main processes that actually run according to a schedule, including strategy "
"execution, order placement, and log writing, are the core of the operation."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "交易员席位：您进 Shell 对话的对象"
msgstr "Trader Seat: The person you interact with in your Shell conversation"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "**Broker（券商）**"
msgstr "**Broker (Securities Firm)**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "接收订单、返回受理结果与成交回报的适配对象"
msgstr ""
"The target audience for receiving orders, returning processing results, and transaction "
"confirmation."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "券商柜台：simulator 是「练习柜台」"
msgstr "Brokerage counter: simulator means \"practice counter\"."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "**mode=0**"
msgstr "**mode=0**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "配置项：表示 live / 模拟实盘（相对回测 mode=1 等）"
msgstr ""
"Configuration item: Indicates live / simulated live trading (relative to backtesting mode=1, etc.)"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "开关：0=按真实时钟跑"
msgstr "Switch: 0 = Runs on real time"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "**CLI**"
msgstr "CLI command"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "命令行交互界面（Trader Shell）"
msgstr "Command-line interactive interface (Trader Shell)"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "打字下指令的「交易员终端」"
msgstr "A \"trader terminal\" for typing commands."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "**TUI**"
msgstr "**TUI**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "图形化终端界面"
msgstr "Graphical terminal interface"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "带面板的全屏界面，与 CLI 二选一"
msgstr "A full-screen interface with a panel, or a CLI option."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:77
msgid "4.2 配置与数据"
msgstr "4.2 Configuration and Data"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:79
msgid ""
"启动 live 前，您通过 `qt.configure(...)` 写入的项会冻结为 **LiveTradeConfig**，并决定资产类型、行情"
"从哪里来、数据如何补齐。本表是配置章 (:doc:`2-configuration-and-run`) 的术语索引。"
msgstr ""
"Before starting LiveTrade, the items you write via `qt.configure(...)` will be frozen as "
"**LiveTradeConfig**, determining the asset types, where market data comes from, and how the data "
"is supplemented. This table is a terminology index for the configuration chapter (:doc:`2-"
"configuration-and-run`)."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "**LiveTradeConfig**"
msgstr "**LiveTradeConfig**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "启动前冻结的一份 live 配置快照，运行中不再被意外改掉"
msgstr ""
"A snapshot of the live configuration is frozen before startup and will not be accidentally "
"modified during runtime."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "起飞前的检查单，签字后不再涂改"
msgstr "The pre-flight inspection form, once signed, should not be altered."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "**asset_type**"
msgstr ""
"The set of names of the historical data to be fetched, if htypes is empty, the system will try to "
"create all possible htypes by basing on the name of the historical data and the freq/asset_type "
"parameter. the input can be str or list: - str: 'open, high, low, close' - list: ['open', 'high', "
"'low', 'close'] - list: ['open', 'high', 'low', 'close'] - list: ['open', 'high', 'low', 'close'] "
"'high', 'low', 'close']"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "资产类型，如 `E`（股票）、`FD`（场内基金/ETF）"
msgstr "Asset types, such as `E` (stocks) and `FD` (exchange-traded funds/ETFs)."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "告诉系统「这批标的按哪套规则交易」"
msgstr "Tell the system \"which set of rules applies to the trading of this batch of assets\"."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "**refill**"
msgstr "Market conditions and refill"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "从网络渠道补齐本地数据源缺失表/区间"
msgstr "Fill in the missing tables/ranges in the local data source from online channels."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "给本地「数据仓库」补货"
msgstr "Replenishing the local \"data warehouse\""

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "**live 行情频率**"
msgstr "**Live Market Frequency**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "如 `live_price_acquire_freq='15MIN'`，多久拉一次实时价"
msgstr ""
"For example, `live_price_acquire_freq='15MIN'` specifies how often the real-time price is "
"retrieved."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "盯盘刷新间隔"
msgstr "Market monitoring refresh interval"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "**simulator**"
msgstr "``simulator''"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "默认模拟券商类型，用 live 价模拟成交"
msgstr "The default simulated brokerage type uses live pricing to simulate transactions."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "paper trading 柜台"
msgstr "paper trading counter"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:89
msgid "4.3 订单与风控"
msgstr "4.3 Orders and Risk Control"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md:91
msgid ""
"从策略信号到成交，中间经过「本地风控 → 券商受理 → 异步成交」。本表是 :doc:`3-risk-and-order-"
"lifecycle` 的核心词汇；**务必分清「风控拒单」与「柜台拒单」两行**。"
msgstr ""
"From strategy signal to execution, the process involves \"local risk control → brokerage "
"processing → asynchronous execution\". This table contains the core vocabulary of :doc:`3-risk-and-"
"order-lifecycle`; **Please be sure to distinguish between the \"risk control rejection\" and "
"\"counter rejection\" rows.**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "**OrderIntent（订单意图）**"
msgstr "**OrderIntent**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "一笔打算下的单：标的、方向、数量、价格等"
msgstr "A planned order: subject matter, direction, quantity, price, etc."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "填好的委托单草稿"
msgstr "Draft of completed authorization form"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "**AccountSnapshot（账户快照）**"
msgstr "**Account Snapshot**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "评估风控那一刻的现金、持仓、当日成交额等"
msgstr "Cash, open positions, and daily trading volume at the moment of risk assessment"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "下单瞬间的账户「定格照片」"
msgstr "A snapshot of the account at the moment the order was placed."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "**RiskManager（风控管理器）**"
msgstr "**RiskManager**"

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "按顺序执行多条规则，决定是否放行"
msgstr "Execute multiple rules sequentially to determine whether to allow passage."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
msgid "复核台：任一规则不通过则拒单"
msgstr "Review Desk: Orders will be rejected if any rule fails to meet the requirements."

#: ../../source/live_trading/1-overview.md
